						<p>Pāṇḍya, Jaṭāvarman Sundarapāṇḍya, 18th year = c. 13th Century.</p>						

						<p>An Ādittadēvar Mullaikkuḍaiyāṉ seems to have gifted the pāḍikāval right on his land to the temple of Tirukkunṟākkuḍi-uḍaiya-nāyaṉār in Vaḍa-panaṅgāḍu-nāḍu in Jeyasiṅgakulakāla-vaḷanāḍu.</p>						

